---
title: Grilled BBQ Pork Sandwiches with Creamy Slaw
description: Inspired by everyone's favourite BBQ rib sammie, this pork chop version hits all the right notes with dill pickles, crisp onions and a refreshing side of slaw! Grab the napkins and dig in!
